  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "para_id": "Q001767.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Mešlamta-ea , the master , the right hand of Lagaš , Kilula , the throne-bearer , child of Ur-Bagara , fashioned ( this seal ) for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim . The name of this seal is \" My master , let me live in his benevolent attention .\""
    }
  ],
